OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud will gradually spread
OL,6,Faround coastal areas of Devon and
OL,7,FCornwall through the day today. A
OL,8,Fbright start elsewhere with
OL,9,Fincreasingly cloudy skies. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying mostly cloudy and
OL,13,Fmurky overnight, although some clear
OL,14,Fspells are possible at times. Mist and
OL,15,Ffog patches may form in any clearer
OL,16,Finterludes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
