OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA few bright spells to start
OL,6,Fthe day, but cloud quickly thickening
OL,7,Fagain during the morning as heavy
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain move in from the
OL,9,Fwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fdrier picture over the next few days
OL,13,Fwith some warm spells of sunshine.
OL,14,FSunshine will be hazy at times and it
OL,15,Fwill feel increasingly humid.
